        <img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.britannica.com/s:300x300/71/21771-050-099E3131/marble-herm-Euripides-original-Greek-Museo-Archeologico-330-bce.jpg" alt="Euripides, marble herm copied from a Greek original, c. 340–330 bce; in the Museo Archeologico Nazionale, Naples."    />
    

